room_title: Escape room "The Study" by The Ville Escape Room in Kirksville
room_description: The Study is owned by Dr. Rupert K. Rollins. He is an archaeology professor at Harvard University. Rumor has it that on his last expedition he stole some very valuable diamonds from Egypt. You have one hour to try and steal these precious diamonds from him before he gets back from teaching his class. Do you think you have what it takes to outwit Dr. Rollins and get the diamonds?â€‹
